  "detailed_description": "<strong>Altitude's Toll is a short single-player walking simulator mystery set in Himalayas.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2>Matt, a 27 year old sherpa, is solving a mystery with his dispatcher about a magnetic repulsion in Himalayas. The dispatcher is thinking about leaving the job as it isn't fulfilling enough; on the other hand, Matt is enjoying it...<br>...until something unsettling happens on his final ascend.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719980/extras/b49430175e2fb729c325fb98aebe7c35.poster.avif?t=1709125249\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719980/extras/b49430175e2fb729c325fb98aebe7c35.webm?t=1709125249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719980/extras/b49430175e2fb729c325fb98aebe7c35.mp4?t=1709125249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pretty and colorful nature<br></li><li> Slow immersive gameplay<br></li><li> Wildlife reacts to the players presence<br></li><li> Delivering packages<br></li><li> Handmade level design<br></li><li> Explorable world</li></ul><br>Playtime 30-60 minutes",
